	<!--
		How looting Rings work:
		If a lootable object (chest / stash / forge / zbag) can provide a Ring as loot:
			1) If it does NOT have a loot_prob_template, it will have a 20% chance to provide a RINGS
			2) If it DOES have a loot_prob_template, it has a 20% chance to THEN roll the loot_prob_template's % chance.
			
		So basically, sections with loot_prob_template are harder to receive a Ring item from.
	-->
	

